    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people want to help, but it doesn't change the fact that the person i actually need is gone. it's like i'm just a ghost walking through a life that doesn't belong to me anymore. everything feels so heavy and pointless, like i'm just waiting for something to end.",
